1. *Pokaži* mi kako to radiš. (Show me how you do it.)
2. Ako nešto ne razumeš, samo mi *pokaži* prstom. (If you don't understand something, just *point* to it for me.)
3. *Pokaži* svoje znanje na testu. (Demonstrate your knowledge on the test.)
4. *Pokazao* je svoju hrabrost u borbi. (He *showed* his bravery in the fight.)
5. Kada *pokazuješ* na nekoga, uvek imaj u vidu da tri prsta upireš u sebe. (When you *point* at someone, always remember that three fingers are pointing back at yourself.)
6. Ukoliko *pokazuješ* poštovanje, bićeš poštovan. (If you *show* respect, you will be respected.)
7. *Pokazala* mi je svoj novi auto. (She *showed* me her new car.)
8. Nisam mislio da će on *pokazati* toliko interesovanja za ovaj posao. (I didn't think he would *show* so much interest in this job.)
9. Moraš *pokazati* malo više strpljenja. (You have to *show* a little more patience.)
10. Oni su *pokazali* da su spremni za velike stvari. (They *demonstrated* that they are ready for big things.)